{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">An Open-World to Explore</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover a quiet island town racked by corruption, conspiracy, and collusion. Alone or with up to 3 of your friends, explore speakeasies, tea houses, dockyards, and more across Peagrove's 8 unique districts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339630/extras/TownHallEA1.png?t=1731955484\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Meet the Locals</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in a world of colourful characters, risky rogues, and vainglorious villains. Townsfolk will remember you and your actions, so find friends, make enemies, and integrate into the local culture as Peagrove's newest detective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339630/extras/charactersEATeaser.png?t=1731955484\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Powered by Unreal Engine 5</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Old meets new with retro pixel art graphics and the latest lighting and networking technology powered by Unreal Engine 5. With dynamically lit scenery and hand crafted portraits, experience a high fidelity detective adventure from start to finish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339630/extras/CoffeeShopEA1.png?t=1731955484\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339630/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731955484","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339630/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1731955484","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339630/6aa5380f27eb9f5638cc214ae